location: Code & Cafe, 4304 Rue Saint-Denis, Montreal, QC
title: 002 - Implementing Vue.js In Legacy Code

datas.title: Vue in a legacy application - How we did it at Alayacare
datas.author: Stéphane Reiss
datas.description: Stéphane is a full-stack web developer, working at Alayacare, he contributed to the frontend transformation, from a legacy application to Vue components. He will show us how Vue.js was introduced and share the goods and the bads he learned along the way.

datas.title: How to integrate JQuery plugins with Vue
datas.author: Luiz Brandao
datas.description: Luiz will explain how to integrate a JQuery plugin into a Vue.js app.
